### --- Enterprise: Team Management ---

GET {{baseUrl}}/enterprise/team/departments
Authorization: Bearer {{enterpriseToken}}

###

GET {{baseUrl}}/enterprise/team/employees
Authorization: Bearer {{enterpriseToken}}

###

GET {{baseUrl}}/enterprise/team/employees?department=Engineering&employmentStatus=active&search=rahul
Authorization: Bearer {{enterpriseToken}}

###

GET {{baseUrl}}/enterprise/team/employees/{{employeeId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{enterpriseToken}}

###

### --- Enterprise: Access Requests ---

GET {{baseUrl}}/enterprise/access-requests
Authorization: Bearer {{enterpriseToken}}

###

GET {{baseUrl}}/enterprise/access-requests?status=pending
Authorization: Bearer {{enterpriseToken}}

###

POST {{baseUrl}}/enterprise/access-requests
Authorization: Bearer {{enterpriseToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employeeUserId": "EMPLOYEE_USER_ID_HERE",
  "requestType": "profile_access",
  "message": "We need your profile for compliance review."
}

###

### --- Enterprise: Company Insights ---

GET {{baseUrl}}/enterprise/insights
Authorization: Bearer {{enterpriseToken}}

###

### --- Company: Employee Linking ---

